.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-SWEEP\-SUBMIT" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-sweep\-submit \- Submit all trials in an embedded sweep
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose sweep submit [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Expand the top\-level sweep block, render one batch script per trial, submit each trial as an independent Slurm job, and persist a sweep manifest.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read; if omitted, use the active context compose file or fall back to compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--dry\-run\fR
Validate and print the expanded trials without writing scripts or submitting jobs.
.TP
\fB--max\-trials\fR \fIN\fR
Maximum number of trials allowed for this submission; defaults to 100.
.TP
\fB--skip\-prepare\fR
Skip image preparation and reuse existing artifacts.
.TP
\fB--force\-rebuild\fR
Refresh imported and prepared artifacts before submission.
.TP
\fB--no\-preflight\fR
Skip the preflight phase before submission.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--sbatch\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sbatch executable. Default: sbatch.
.TP
\fB--srun\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the srun executable. Default: srun.
.TP
\fB--scontrol\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the scontrol executable. Default: scontrol.
.TP
\fB--enroot\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the enroot executable. Default: enroot.
.TP
\fB--apptainer\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the apptainer executable. Default: apptainer.
.TP
\fB--singularity\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the singularity executable. Default: singularity.
.TP
\fB--huggingface\-cli\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the huggingface\-cli executable used by hf:// stage\-in trials. Default: huggingface\-cli.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose sweep submit \-f train.yaml \-\-dry\-run
hpc\-compose sweep submit \-f train.yaml
hpc\-compose sweep status \-f train.yaml
hpc\-compose sweep list \-f train.yaml
.fi
